eolDate: Offical Cats project is no longer maintained.
description:
Blender versions 3.1 to 3.5 work best with the development (dev) version of the Cats add-on.

If you plan to use a Blender version in the 3.x series, we highly recommend using either Blender 3.3 or 3.6, as these are Long Term Support (LTS) versions.

Support and assistance are available on the official Cats add-on Discord server.
